<PROFILE>_AN-EK3EKAF8FT</PROFILE>
<DATE>941130
</DATE>
<HEADLINE>
FT  30 NOV 94 / Budget 94 (Their Budget): Brewery executive
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
