<HEADLINE>
FT  30 NOV 94 / Budget 94 (Government Statements): Education spending set to
rise by 4% to Pounds 11bn
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Education secretary Gillian Shephard announced a Pounds 427m increase in
government spending on education. The budgets of the Department for
Education and Ofsted will total almost Pounds 11bn with a 4 per cent rise -
