FT  30 NOV 94 / Howard aide is arrested
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
A personal assistant to Mr Michael Howard, the home secretary, has been
suspended after being arrested for allegedly breaching Scotland Yard
security and taking a Special Branch car.
Ms Janine Barnes is reported to have walked into the underground car park
beneath Scotland Yard after a row with one of Mr Howard's bodyguards. She
was not stopped when she drove an unmarked Special Branch car out of the
building.
