last meeting broke down in a row over the Palestinians' inclusion of
Jerusalem in projects to be backed.
In October last year, aid donors pledged more than Dollars 2bn over five
years for projects to support Palestinian self-rule, with Dollars 700m to be
paid out this year. Only about Dollars 60m had so far been received.
